<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Hidden Valley</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Nestled within a tranquil location on the northern edge of the city of Calgary, is a quiet and scenic residential neighborhood known as the Hidden Valley. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">With its well-planned landscape, immaculate greens, and idyllic surroundings, the community in Hidden Valley is coveted by young couples, growing families and the elderly alike. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Residents in Hidden Valley Real Estate have convenient access to everything from playgrounds to shopping complexes and a variety of recreational venues.</p>
